          description: List of users with pagination info

            X-RateLimit-Remaining:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: Requests remaining in current window
            X-RateLimit-Reset:
              schema:
                type: integer
              description: Seconds until rate limit resets

components:
  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 123
        email:
          type: string
          format: email
          example: "john@example.com"
        name:
          type: string
          example: "John Doe"
        shippingAddress:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Address'
        createdAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
        updatedAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
      required:
        - id
        - email
        - name
        - shippingAddress
        - createdAt
        - updatedAt

    Product:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 456
        name:
          type: string
          example: "Wireless Headphones"
        description:
          type: string
          example: "High-quality wireless headphones with noise cancellation"
        price:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 199.99
        category:
          type: string
          example: "electronics"
        stockCount:
          type: integer
          example: 50
        createdAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
        updatedAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - description
        - price
        - category
        - stockCount
        - createdAt
        - updatedAt

    Order:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          example: 789
        userId:
          type: integer
          example: 123
        items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/OrderItem'
          example:
            - productId: 456
              quantity: 2
              unitPrice: 199.99
            - productId: 789
              quantity: 1
              unitPrice: 49.99
        total:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 449.97
        status:
          type: string
          enum:
            - pending
            - confirmed
            - shipped
            - delivered
            - cancelled
          example: "pending"
        createdAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
        updatedAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
      required:
        - id
        - userId
        - items
        - total
        - status
        - createdAt
        - updatedAt

    OrderItem:
      type: object
      properties:
        productId:
          type: integer
          example: 456
        quantity:
          type: integer
          minimum: 1
          example: 2
        unitPrice:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 199.99
      required:
        - productId
        - quantity
        - unitPrice

    Address:
      type: object
      properties:
        street:
          type: string
          example: "123 Main Street"
        city:
          type: string
          example: "New York"
        state:
          type: string
          example: "NY"
        postalCode:
          type: string
          example: "10001"
        country:
          type: string
          example: "USA"
      required:
        - street
        - city
        - state
        - postalCode
        - country

    ProblemDetail:
      type: object
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          format: uri
          example: "https://api.ecommerce.example.com/errors/validation-error"
        title:
          type: string
          example: "Validation Error"
        status:
          type: integer
          example: 400
        detail:
          type: string
          example: "The request body contains invalid data"
        instance:
          type: string
          format: uri
          example: "/orders"
      required:
        - type
        - title
        - status
